05:19.194 --> 05:22.186
- Will you just give me a couple hours?
- Give me a break.

05:23.073 --> 05:26.361
Look, I'm saying I'll have it. I just need...

05:26.451 --> 05:29.944
I'll have it today. All right? Just tell her that.

05:30.038 --> 05:32.871
