06:03.446 --> 06:04.436
Ariel, stop it.

06:06.992 --> 06:08.983
Come on, let's get your shoes on.

06:09.077 --> 06:11.068
We're gonna make a stop
before you get to school.

06:12.330 --> 06:14.287
<i>We can expect light onshore wind</i>

06:14.374 --> 06:17.537
<i>coupled with an upper level
low pressure drop off the coast</i>

06:17.627 --> 06:21.586
