06:37.689 --> 06:40.977
Lady! Listen. Hey, hey.
Look, you're in my parking spot.

06:41.067 --> 06:43.274
Oh, really. Well, you know what?
I'll just be one second.

06:43.361 --> 06:46.649
- Lady, I got a conference call I gotta get to...
- I haven't got time for this right now!

06:46.740 --> 06:47.946
