07:02.547 --> 07:04.208
- Hey! Hey!
- Walter!

07:04.299 --> 07:07.462
That mouth of yours
is gonna get you killed, man.

07:09.679 --> 07:12.137
Hey, Kat. Yeah, man, this is Walt Deeds.

07:12.223 --> 07:15.636
Listen, I need a tow truck in the parking lot.
Some lady parked in my brother's spot.

07:18.021 --> 07:19.386
Thanks.

07:19.481 --> 07:22.473
