08:50.905 --> 08:51.940
I'm sorry, doll.

08:52.032 --> 08:53.773
- No, you're not.
- We gotta fill it quickly.

08:53.867 --> 08:57.076
If you want it,
you'd better tell me about it now.

08:57.829 --> 09:00.070
Do I have a choice?

09:00.165 --> 09:02.372
I gotta take my kid to school.

09:06.296 --> 09:09.459
With Dexter leaving,
where does that put us, John?

09:09.549 --> 09:12.257
Not in the best place.
They were 75% of our profit.

09:12.677 --> 09:16.420
Hold on a second, when did they get
to 75%? Last quarter it was 60.

09:16.514 --> 09:21.429
<i>When Walt offered them a 12% discount
on all new products, they upped their deal.</i>

09:23.521 --> 09:26.934
It was a good idea at the time. Okay, it was!

09:27.734 --> 09:29.145
<i>Fine, we're in it now.</i>

09:29.235 --> 09:32.227
<i>Get every financial bit of information
you can on Brunson.</i>

09:32.655 --> 09:37.400
I'll be burning the midnight oil on this one,
John, so I'll be up in a second.

09:39.871 --> 09:44.240
Wow. Fat Boy Harley. Nice.

09:49.464 --> 09:51.421
You just ought to do that, Wes.

09:53.468 --> 09:55.425
