09:55.512 --> 09:57.298
Get a bike.

09:57.388 --> 09:59.755
Meet up with Rich, Josh, in Mexico.

10:00.183 --> 10:02.800
Were you not just on this conference call?

10:02.894 --> 10:04.384
I got a business to run.

10:04.896 --> 10:06.512
I can run this company.

10:09.400 --> 10:11.061
Oh, you don't think I can run the business?

10:11.152 --> 10:12.734
- Walter.
- What?

10:13.988 --> 10:18.027
Wesley, this wasn't even your dream.
It was mine.

10:18.118 --> 10:21.907
- I can run this company, man.
- How about you show me?

10:21.996 --> 10:23.862
Stop saying it, just show me.

10:23.957 --> 10:26.699
Oh, no. Hey. Hey!

10:26.835 --> 10:29.497
- No, come on, please.
- Here she comes.

10:29.587 --> 10:32.500
I'm sorry, lady. You were parked illegally.

10:33.842 --> 10:35.458
You made him tow my car?

10:35.552 --> 10:36.792
You parked in his spot, lady.

10:36.886 --> 10:38.251
I'm not talking to you, midget!

10:38.596 --> 10:40.178
I'm talking to this ass.

10:40.974 --> 10:42.840
- Ass?
- Yeah, you heard me.

10:43.184 --> 10:45.926
