find somewhere else to park.

11:44.495 --> 11:45.701
Put it down, Frank.

11:48.166 --> 11:50.658
Jillian, just park my car, okay?
I think my iPad's in the back.

11:51.002 --> 11:52.709
You just sit down.

11:55.840 --> 11:57.080
Ass!

11:58.092 --> 12:01.505
- You see? Move, man!
- Walter, it's handled!

12:01.596 --> 12:03.086
