I'm gonna handle it!

12:03.181 --> 12:07.266
- I ain't gonna let her call you an ass!
- Get on the elevator, man.

12:08.228 --> 12:10.890
- Come on, man!
- Please.

12:12.941 --> 12:15.057
You like getting walked on?

12:17.153 --> 12:18.359
God.

12:25.453 --> 12:28.445
