17:41.143 --> 17:44.511
Yes. Yes, he is. I make sure of it.

17:45.231 --> 17:48.394
Mom. What's going on?

17:50.278 --> 17:53.771
I read the newspaper. Are we all right?

17:54.615 --> 17:57.824
