46:04.178 --> 46:06.385
So this is it, you know?

46:08.182 --> 46:12.050
Okay, knock around back at 11:00,
ask for Jerry.

46:12.144 --> 46:14.306
Tell him Denise said
it was okay for you to stay.

46:15.273 --> 46:17.560
And, honey, this is no hotel.

46:17.650 --> 46:21.518
Keep your belongings close
and your daughter closer, you hear?

46:22.154 --> 46:23.485
Thank you.

46:25.032 --> 46:26.363
- First name?
- Lauren.

46:26.450 --> 46:28.316
Go in.

46:28.411 --> 46:29.776
- Lonnie.
- Go on in.

46:29.870 --> 46:30.860
