47:08.743 --> 47:11.656
I don't want my mommy to get into trouble.

47:14.040 --> 47:16.372
She won't get in any trouble.

47:19.587 --> 47:21.874
We sleep in the car.

47:33.768 --> 47:36.886
It's okay, I'm here. I'm here.
Thank you for waiting, really.

47:36.979 --> 47:39.346
Can I talk to you for a second?

47:40.566 --> 47:41.772
It's not a great day.

47:41.859 --> 47:45.523
