49:26.297 --> 49:29.881
Please, please, listen. No, no, no.
I want to talk to you forjust a second.

49:30.301 --> 49:32.633
- Please, just let me go!
- No, no.

49:33.679 --> 49:36.387
She's in my office. No, no, Lindsey. Lindsey.

49:36.682 --> 49:39.265
