- Lindsey, Lindsey.

49:39.477 --> 49:41.184
- She knows not to...
- Listen.

49:42.688 --> 49:44.975
She didn't move, I found her.
I made her come with me, okay?

49:45.065 --> 49:46.055
She didn't leave.

49:46.192 --> 49:48.274
Oh, God, did you call Child Welfare?

49:49.320 --> 49:52.529
- No.
- Thank you. Thank you.

49:53.699 --> 49:54.860
