50:14.512 --> 50:15.502
No, we don't have family.

50:15.596 --> 50:17.382
Don't you think
I would have done that already?

50:18.140 --> 50:21.758
What about this boyfriend, the one
that was gonna help you with the car?

50:24.605 --> 50:26.061
We broke up.

50:27.691 --> 50:29.022
- Is that the truth?
- Can you let me go to my kid?

50:29.109 --> 50:31.771
No, no, no. Look.

50:32.446 --> 50:35.359
I had to drag her out of that closet.
She was scared to death.

50:35.449 --> 50:37.315
Shaking. Because she was so worried about

50:37.409 --> 50:40.071
what you would say
or what you would do to her.

50:40.913 --> 50:42.278
