51:17.283 --> 51:19.866
I want you to calm down,
'cause I've had just about enough of you...

51:19.952 --> 51:22.319
- You just don't understand.
-...this talk about me and my privilege...

51:22.413 --> 51:25.371
- We live in the real world.
-...and where I come from. And I don't?

51:25.457 --> 51:26.947
No, you do not.

51:28.836 --> 51:31.669
Tell me,
how much does a gallon of milk cost?

51:34.842 --> 51:37.004
You don't even know.

51:37.094 --> 51:38.801
Or a gallon of gas.

51:39.638 --> 51:42.471
When's the last time
you worried about paying a bill?

51:44.852 --> 51:46.013
Ariel.

51:46.979 --> 51:48.435
You're not...

51:54.820 --> 51:57.278
- Come on.
- I'm tired.

52:13.631 --> 52:15.042
- Lindsey?
- Yeah, Jerry?

52:15.132 --> 52:16.748
Yeah, come on in.

52:21.639 --> 52:23.676
Just follow me, all right?

52:26.685 --> 52:28.892
Look, it's lights out,
so you want to be quiet, okay?

52:28.979 --> 52:30.435
