53:36.588 --> 53:39.125
Yeah, there's a lot going on at the office.

53:39.883 --> 53:41.248
You want to talk about it?

53:41.760 --> 53:44.092
No. I'll get it all worked out.

53:47.766 --> 53:49.677
You were pretty drunk last night.

53:50.769 --> 53:51.884
