53:52.438 --> 53:54.645
Don't apologize. I was just...

53:57.860 --> 53:59.692
I don't think I've ever seen you that drunk.

53:59.778 --> 54:02.861
I don't think
I've ever been that drunk before.

54:03.782 --> 54:04.943
