I just wanted to let my hair down.

54:16.754 --> 54:19.587
- Anything I can do?
- No, baby, I'll...

54:20.132 --> 54:22.874
I'm gonna be fine, don't worry about me.

54:23.385 --> 54:24.625
Dang it!

54:26.054 --> 54:27.465
What's that?

54:29.808 --> 54:31.298
- Really?
- What?

54:36.023 --> 54:37.104
